combtxt:LOCAL POLICE CONTACTED THE RAILROAD ON 10/13/13 IN REGARDS TO AN IMPACT THAT OCCURRED AT THE LETENDR E AVE. CROSSING. A FEMALE DRIVER HAD HIT A RAILCAR NEAR THE REAR OF THE TRAIN AND THEN LEFT THE SCEN E. NO INJURIES WERE REPORTED. CREW WAS UNAWARE OF THE INCIDENT AT THE TIME. THERE IS NO INFORMATION ON WHERE IN THE TRAIN THE IMPACT TOOK PLACE. :inci
